org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.graphs

Class XYGraph

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pvg.plasmagraph.utils.graphs.XYGraph
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Graph

    public class XYGraph
extends Object
implements Graph

    Graph class. Contains the methods required to take in numerical coordinate data that the rest of the system may provide it and shape it into a proper XY Scatterplot Graph according to the settings in the Template.

    Author:
    Plasma Visualization Group
